&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a Senior Product Designer to help shape the future of Datadog’s design ecosystem across our suite of products and platform experiences. You’ll play a key role in crafting cohesive, user-centered solutions that empower customers to visualize, monitor, and optimize their systems with confidence.&amp;nbsp;You’ll collaborate closely with engineers, product managers, and designers across multiple teams to simplify complex workflows and create elegant, scalable design solutions that span our 70+ products.At Datadog, we value the relationships and creativity that thrive in our office culture. We operate as a hybrid workplace to help our Datadogs build a work-life harmony that fits them best.&lt;/p&gt;
